What you need to know:

Though entries were still being received from the various clubs in Mount Kenya region, over 50 pairs are expected to battle it out for the five slots reserved for the regionThe top three pairs during the national finals, will travel to Portugal for the World finals from October 26 to 30Meanwhile, Nyali Golf and Country Club in Mombasa will be staging the ongoing NCBA golf series where a field over 200 players were drawn